        <h2>Synopsis</h2>
        <div class="synopsis">
            <p>The series will revolve around <span class="bold">Park Hoon</span>, a South Korean who was captured with his father and grew up in North Korea. He is trained to become a genius doctor, and though Park Hoon lands a job at the best South Korean hospital after defecting, he is treated as a "foreigner." To find his lost North Korean first love, Song Jae Hee, he does anything to make money.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Main Cast</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Lee Jong Suk as Park Hoon</li>
            <li>Goo Seung Hyun as child Park Hoon</li>
            <li>Jin Se Yun as Song Jae Hee / Han Seung Hee</li>
            <li>Seo Ji Hee as child Song Jae Hee</li>
            <li>Park Hae Jin as Han Jae Joon / Lee Sung Hoon</li>
            <li>Kim Ji Hoon as child Han Jae Joon</li>
            <li>Kang So Ra as Oh Soo Hyun</li>
            <li>Shin Soo Yun as child Oh Soo Hyun</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Awards</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>2014 SBS Drama Awards: Top Ten Stars Award, Special Award (Lee Jong Suk)</li>
            <li>2014 APAN Star Awards: Popularity Award (Jin Se Yun)</li>
        </ul>
